{
  "texts": [
    "The Quick Response Code (QR Code)-like structure was abstracted into a binary string and updated by GA [80].",
    "(d) Flowchart of particle swarm optimization algorithm combined with Array Pattern Synthesis (APS).",
    "PSO evacuated the fitness and then updated particle velocity and population location.",
    "APS calculated radar cross section as fitness and returned to PSO module [86].",
    "Reproduced courtesy of The Electromagnetics Academy."
  ]
}